sub_title: Head of Revenue & Channel Management at Corporate Housing Factory and Servicedapartments.nl
summary:
Loving to explore new places and cultures I went on a 5-month back-packing trip just after graduating Hotelschool The Hague and ended up finding a job aligned with my passion for the hospitality industry in Bogot√°, Colombia. 

After more than 10 years of incredible experiences through diverse roles at different chain hotels in Front Office, Marketing and eventually General Management, I am now leading all that has to do with revenue, distribution and channel management, scalability of requests and growth and expansion of all labels at The Corporate Housing Factory.
